data.title: Cher - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Cher: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Born Cherilyn Sarkisian, she is known as the Goddess of Pop. Cher has sold over 100 million records and won Billboard's Artist of the Year Award in 2002.

Before Fame

She was put into foster care when her parents became unable to take care of her. She later gained fame as a member of the duo Sonny & Cher with Sonny Bono.

Trivia

Her Farewell Tour, which ran from 2002 to 2005, had more than 300 stops and grossed over $200 million.

Family Life

She married Sonny Bono on October 27, 1964 and they divorced in 1975. Subsequently, she married her second husband Gregg Allman on June 30, 1975 and they divorced in 1979. She had children named Chaz Bono and Elijah Blue Allman. She began dating Alexander Edwards in late 2022, but they broke up in April 2023.

Associated With

She starred with Christina Aguilera in the 2010 musical film Burlesque.
